message: "If you use this code or dataset, please cite our paper."
title: "ECA Noise Identification — LLM & Transformer Benchmark"
abstract: >
  A benchmark repository for studying rule and noise-parameter identification
  in Elementary Cellular Automata (ECA) under four distinct noise models
  (alpha-asynchronous, s-skewed, stochastic, temporal stochastic), using
  both purpose-built transformer architectures and large language models.
authors:
  - name: "Anonymous Authors"
